      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> to the dish with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p>",
