    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped apple </strong>and <strong>onion wedges</strong> with the <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and give everything a good stir</p><p>Add your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[350ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
