      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and stir through with your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then put the dish in the oven, uncovered, for 25-30 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Normandy-style chicken breast & apple casserole</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
